<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alison-wilson> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Alison Wilson is Regional Director for Yorkshire and the Humber. She was previously at His Majesty’s Treasury where she was leading work to establish the Darlington Economic Campus. Prior to that, Alison was the head of DfE ’s Vulnerable Children Unit. Earlier in her career, Alison has also worked on: opportunity areas the academies programme policy and reform work in both school funding and special education needs"@en .
